    xvimagesink or filesink. It is a layer on top of :class:`GstElement` that provides a
    simplified interface to plugin writers. :class:`GstBase.BaseSink` handles many details
    for you, for example: preroll, clock synchronization, state changes,
    activation in push or pull mode, and queries.

